{
    "Description": "<h3>Usage</h3><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\">component.stop()\n</pre><p><br></p><h3>Notes</h3><ul><li>This requests the component to stop, it doesn't force an immediate stop.</li></ul><p><br></p><h3>Example</h3><pre class=\"ql-syntax\" spellcheck=\"false\">-- Stops the component after 3 seconds\nfunction main(Data)\n   util.sleep(3000)\n   component.stop()\nend\n</pre>",
    "Name": "component.stop",
    "Parameters": null,
    "ParameterTable": false,
    "SummaryLine": "Stops the current component"
}